Synopsis: Retrieves information about startup programs on a remote computer.
Description: The Get-ComputerStartup function retrieves information about startup programs on a specified computer using CIM/WMI.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Get-ComputerStartup -ComputerName "RemoteComputer" -Protocol Wsman
Retrieves startup program information from a remote computer using the Wsman protocol.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 2
Examples.Code:
Get-ComputerStartup -All
Retrieves all startup program information from the local computer.
